Laurent.message: Hey! Ready to start the game?
Put the green cup on the blue square mat at the left centre of the table
Put the orange cup on the blue circle mat at the left middle top of the table
Put the green whole apple on the orange circle mat at the right middle top of the table
Put the green sliced apple on the orange circle mat at the right middle centre of the table
Put the brown bowl on the indigo square mat at the far right top of the table
Put the silver pan on the violet square mat at the far right bottom of the table
Congratulations. We are done with the game. Thanks for playing
